              ],
              "free_text": [
                ".Calculation of asymmetry coefficients.",
                "Asymmetry coefficients obtained by other authors were",
                "systematized for two cases.",
                "A) En-gamma-max = 22 MeV and E > 5.5 MeV.",
                "B) En-gamma-max = 34 MeV and E > 8 MeV."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The angular distributions were approximated with",
                "formula A + B*sin**2 + C*cos .",
                "The asymmetry observable for different energy groups",
                "of photoneutrons is discussed relative to 90 degree",
                "to the gamma-quanta beam."
